Kyle Downes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kyle_Downes 0 Kyle Downes (born March 18, 1983 in Summertown, Tennessee) is a Canadian-American actor, best known for his recurring role as Larry Tudgeman in the Disney Channel Original Series Lizzie McGuire and his characterization of Ezra Friedken in Higher Ground. His other television acting credits include Are You Afraid of the Dark?, Boston Public, CSI: Miami, The Famous Jett Jackson, The L Word, Goosebumps and La Femme Nikita.
